definitions.definition: Sexually and/or romantically attracted to members of the same sex, such as a man who is attracted to men or a woman who is attracted to women; gay . ( Typically used in the sense of sole/exclusive attraction. )
examples: No, it wouldn't make a difference if the applicant was homosexual .
labels: of a person or other animal
definitions.label_groups: of a person or other animal , formal , distancing or dated

definitions.definition: Between two people of the same sex; gay .
examples: Most western countries have repealed laws against homosexual activity between consenting adults.
labels: of a romantic or sexual act or relationship
definitions.label_groups: of a romantic or sexual act or relationship , formal , distancing or dated

definitions.definition: Intended for or used by homosexuals, as a nightclub , a bar , etc.
